  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nCurrently a validator does not know when it will need to perform its responsibilities until the moment the slot arrives. We actually know this information as early as a cycle transition, so we can leverage this in order to notify validators way in advance of their role. Say, if a validator is selected to propose 20 slots from now, we can warn them 10 slots before their assignment. Logs can suffice for now.\r\n",
